*{{cite news |date=31 January 2021 |title='PSG Star Neymar Is The Best Player In The World Ahead Of Lionel Messi And Cristiano Ronaldo' |url=https://www.sportbible.com/football/news-neymar-is-the-best-player-in-the-world-ahead-of-messi-and-ronaldo-20210131 |access-date=7 November 2021 |newspaper=[[SPORTbible]]}}
